query:
CREATE TABLE `adminSettings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `adminUserId` int NOT NULL,
  `settingKey` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `settingValue` json NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT (now()) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `adminSettings_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `uq_adminSettings_user_key` UNIQUE(`adminUserId`, `settingKey`),
  INDEX `idx_adminSettings_adminUserId` (`adminUserId`),
  CONSTRAINT `adminSettings_adminUserId_users_id_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`adminUserId`) REFERENCES `users`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
